✅ 1. LOGGING — “Diary of your application”
Logging means your app writes down everything important that happens — like a diary or CCTV footage.

✅ 2. BACKGROUND TASKS — “Do it later while user is free”
Background tasks mean the user gets the response quickly, and the heavy work continues in the background after the response is sent.

