4.Axios

What it is: A tool for making API calls.

Better than fetch: Easy syntax, handles JSON automatically, can add headers like tokens.

axios.get('/tasks', { headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` } })


Analogy: Axios = VIP waiter who understands special requests easily.
